    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera (996.2) represents a pinnacle of analog driver engagement. Featuring the 3.6L M96 flat-six powerplant, the engine has undergone a comprehensive IMS bearing retrofit and RMS replacement to ensure mechanical longevity. The 6-speed G96 transaxle delivers crisp, tactile engagement, complemented by a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The chassis remains taut with zero bushing deflection, providing exceptional lateral stability. The exterior boasts original paint with no swirling or rock chips, while the undercarriage is pristine and free of oxidation or fluid seepage. This is a turn-key example for the discerning collector seeking peak atmospheric performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
