    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that defies its age. This car has been preserved in showroom condition, having been strictly garage-kept and professionally detailed on a monthly basis. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely zero swirl marks, dings, or stone chips. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of any wear or creasing, and the 'new car' scent is still subtly present. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach. Every service has been performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships, with a complete logbook included. From the pristine engine bay to the untouched alloy wheels wrapped in fresh, top-tier tires, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class. It drives as smoothly and silently as the day it left the factory. For the discerning collector or buyer who demands nothing less than perfection, this is the one.",
      "price": 48500.0,
